Dialogue: 5,0:00:00.76,0:00:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,During the Kyoho Famine of 1732, \Nmany died of starvation on Hitogashima.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:07.50,0:00:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the island was dying off, \Na whale washed up on Omoto Beach.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.49,0:00:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Overjoyed with this gift from God,\N the islanders gathered to devour it.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.31,0:00:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As a fisherman's daughter came,\N the whale's body suddenly flashed.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.88,0:00:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the blink of an eye, it took the form of that girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:28.52,0:00:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it consumed the girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.18,0:00:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fearing a curse, people worshipped it as the living goddess Hiruko.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the legend of Hiruko, \Npassed down through generations on Hitogashima.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:41.02,0:00:41.02,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:01:00.33,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}It's come to the point where I just want to hoard all your words
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:06.33,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Even the ramblings from your travels are treasures to me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:09.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Whether I sketch or erase it's all torn away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:13.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}That's the price I pay for my awakening
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:18.59,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Or my daydream's tricking me and I'm still lost in the unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:21.76,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Illuminated by the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:24.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Your figure casts a shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.94,0:01:28.07,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}And when that silhouette wavers slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:30.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}That happens to be my cue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:37.87,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}I wish this were fiction but slow motion is how it begins
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:43.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}If the visceral warmth and traces you left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:49.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Are protecting someone's future, I'll play the warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:53.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Amidst pain and sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:56.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}I'll conquer my fears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:59.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}It's a paradox of life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:02.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Or perhaps god's algorithm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:05.77,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}When our tactics overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:10.53,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}We'll be laughing
