Dialogue: 5,0:02:15.29,0:02:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you sense any shadows?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.56,0:02:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.01,0:02:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Nagumo was right.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.97,0:02:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Karikiri ain't a shadow.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.67,0:02:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but don't let yer guard down.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.71,0:02:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:29.15,0:02:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so hot recently.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.27,0:02:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.05,0:02:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Tokyo hotter than Wakayama?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:35.82,0:02:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not much different.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.40,0:02:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have some cold barley tea.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.16,0:02:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.40,0:02:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought you came to Tokyo last year.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:46.14,0:02:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:46.94,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday you told me that you went to a gaming convention in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.72,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! It was near the ocean, in Makuhari.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.19,0:03:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Makuhari is in Chiba, but yer right, Tokyo really was hot!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And the place was just packed!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You like games, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.72,0:03:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What type do you play?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.68,0:03:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to love RPGs,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.33,0:03:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but now it's FPSs on my computer or sim games.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.97,0:03:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going again this year?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.87,0:03:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I probably won't make it this year.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.88,0:03:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really looking forward to the FF7 Remake.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.48,0:03:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear a lot about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never played it before?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.93,0:03:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't born yet when it first came out.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a unique atmosphere.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.59,0:03:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe because it came out at the end of the century.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.48,0:03:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Both its art and music have a post-apocalyptic feeling.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.12,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes ya think about how life on Earth will end.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Life?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.77,0:03:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Games to you are like novels for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.29,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the novel {\i1}Swamp Man{\i0} by Nagumo Ryuunosuke?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.80,0:04:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it so much that it feels like it was \Nwritten about my life—that it's my story.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.22,0:04:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not familiar with that novel, \Nbut I know the Swamp Man thought experiment.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it about that?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
